Package lab5

Class WeatherInfo

java.lang.Object
lab5.WeatherInfo
public class WeatherInfo extends Object
The WeatherInfo class represents information about weather conditions at a specific point in time. It includes data such as the date of upload, wind direction, wind speed, temperature, precipitation, and humidity.
